'''2016年聖帕伯利托市場煙火爆炸'''為2016年12月20日，發生於[[墨西哥城|墨西哥城]]北部的[[圖爾特佩克|圖爾特佩克]]聖帕伯利托市場的煙火爆炸事件<ref name="guardian">{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/dec/20/mexico-fireworks-market-explosion|title=Mexico fireworks market explosion leaves at least 26 dead|publisher=Associated Press|via=''The Guardian''|date=2016-12-20|accessdate=2016-12-20|archive-date=2017-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170912234155/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/dec/20/mexico-fireworks-market-explosion|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-38387239|title='Several killed' in Mexico fireworks blast|publisher=BBC News|date=2016-12-20|accessdate=2016-12-20|archive-date=2017-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170913045416/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-38387239|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/12/20/americas/mexico-fireworks-explosion/|title=Blast at Mexico fireworks market injures dozens|first=Nelson|last=Quinones|publisher=CNN|date=2016-12-20|accessdate=2016-12-20|archive-date=2017-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170913044101/http://www.cnn.com/2016/12/20/americas/mexico-fireworks-explosion/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，造成至少32人死亡，59人受傷，另外有12人失蹤。圖爾特佩克的煙火工業相當發達<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://au.news.yahoo.com/sunday-night/features/a/22228813/festival-of-fire-san-juan-de-dios/#page1|title=Festival of fire: San Juan de Dios|access-date=2016-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161221164321/https://au.news.yahoo.com/sunday-night/features/a/22228813/festival-of-fire-san-juan-de-dios/#page1|archive-date=2016-12-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，該地煙火生產歷史已達200年<ref name="Gudiño">{{cite web|last1=Gudiño|first1=Alondra Ávila y Alejandra|title=Tultepec: más de 65% de la población depende de la pirotecnia|url=http://www.milenio.com/region/Tultepec-poblacion-depende-pirotecnia_0_869913108.html|website=Milenio|accessdate=21 December 2016|archive-date=2017-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170912235303/http://www.milenio.com/region/Tultepec-poblacion-depende-pirotecnia_0_869913108.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，當地人口約65%從事煙火相關產業<ref name="Gudiño" />。聖帕伯利托市場為墨西哥手工煙火的製造中心<ref name="guardian" />，於2005年及2006年發生煙火相關爆炸事件後，已實施新的安全法規<ref name="mirror" />。
